NORTH SEA.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE BY
   M/V WG TASMAN TOWING EIGHT 5200 METER LONG CABLES
   IN AREA BOUND BY
   57-07.9N 001-56.9E, 57-02.1N 002-10.1E,
   56-47.1N 001-46.1E, 56-53.0N 001-33.1E.
   FOUR MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1703/14.
